iatum)))),(((Solanum_evolvulifolium,Solanum_uleanum),((((Solanum_palustre,Solanum_etuberosum),((Solanum_circaeifolium,((((Solanum_leptophyes,Solanum_oplocense),((((Solanum_avilesii,Solanum_okadae),(Solanum_sparsipilum,((Solanum_stoloniferum,(Solanum_spegazzinii,(Solanum_alandiae,Solanum_doddsii))),(Solanum_verrucosum,(Solanum_iopetalum,((Solanum_schenckii,Solanum_incamayoense),(Solanum_hougasii,Solanum_guerreroense))))))),(((Solanum_kurtzianum,Solanum_infundibuliforme),(Solanum_vernei,Solanum_microdontum)),Solanum_ugentii)),((Solanum_chacoense,(Solanum_yungasense,Solanum_arnezii)),Solanum_tarijense))),(((Solanum_demissum,Solanum_acaule),Solanum_albicans),((Solanum_violaceimarmoratum,(((((Solanum_subpanduratum,Solanum_colombianum),Solanum_oxycarpum),Solanum_tundalomense),Solanum_longiconicum),Solanum_agrimonifolium)),(((Solanum_ambosinum,(Solanum_bukasovii,(Solanum_tuberosum,(Solanum_brevicaule,Solanum_marinasense)))),(Solanum_lignicaule,Solanum_achacachense)),((Solanum_santolallae,((Solanum_pampasense,Solanum_raphanifolium),Solanum_laxissimum)),Solanum_candolleanum))))),(Solanum_andreanum,(((Solanum_morelliforme,Solanum_clarum),(((Solanum_ehrenbergii,(Solanum_cardiophyllum,Solanum_bulbocastanum)),(Solanum_jamesii,Solanum_pinnatisectum)),Solanum_polyadenium)),((Solanum_commersonii,((Solanum_multiinterruptum,Solanum_acroscopicum),(Solanum_immite,(Solanum_chomatophilum,Solanum_piurae)))),Solanum_scabrifolium))))),((Solanum_lycopersicoides,(((Solanum_neorickii,Solanum_chmielewskii),((Solanum_chilense,Solanum_peruvianum),(Solanum_humboldti,((Solanum_cheesmaniae,(Solanum_pimpinellifolium,Solanum_lycopersicum_var__cerasiforme)),Solanum_lycopersicum)))),(Solanum_rothii,(Solanum_pennellii,Solanum_habrochaites)))),Solanum_juglandifolium))),(Solanum_trizygum,((Solanum_muricatum,Solanum_fraxinifolium),Solanum_appendiculatum))),Solanum_allophyllum)),((((Solanum_riojense,(Solanum_palitans,Solanum_tripartitum)),(Solanum_caesium,(Solanum_triflorum,((((Solanum_americanum,(Solanum_pt ianum,(Dasyphyllum_latifolium,(Dasyphyllum_velutinum,(Dasyphyllum_sprengelianum,Dasyphyllum_candolleanum)))),Dasyphyllum_reticulatum),(((Dasyphyllum_colombianum,Dasyphyllum_argenteum),((Dasyphyllum_ferox,Dasyphyllum_armatum),Dasyphyllum_popayanense)),((Dasyphyllum_synacanthum,Dasyphyllum_vagans),Dasyphyllum_spinescens))),((Dasyphyllum_brasiliense,Dasyphyllum_inerme),(Dasyphyllum_tomentosum,Dasyphyllum_leptacanthum)))),((Dasyphyllum_diacanthoides,(Dasyphyllum_excelsum,Dasyphyllum_dicanthoides)),((Arnaldoa_weberbaueri,Arnaldoa_macbrideana),Fulcaldea_laurifolia))),(Huarpea_andina,(Barnadesia_parviflora,(Barnadesia_jelskii,((Barnadesia_lehmannii,(Barnadesia_dombeyana,((Barnadesia_glomerata,Barnadesia_polyacantha),(Barnadesia_caryophylla,Barnadesia_odorata)))),(Barnadesia_pycnophylla,(Barnadesia_spinosa,Barnadesia_arborea)))))))))),(((((Tarchonanthus_camphoratus,((Ericentrodea_corazonensis,Ericentrodea_decomposita),Brachylaena_discolor)),(Brachylaena_neriifolia,Brachylaena_elliptica)),(Oldenburgia_intermedia,Oldenburgia_grandis)),(Brachylaena_huillensis,((((((Atractylodes_chinensis,(Atractylodes_lancea_x_Atractylodes_chinensis,Atractylodes_koreana)),Atractylodes_lancea_subsp__luotianensis),Atractylodes_lancea),(((Atractylis_cancellata,(Thevenotia_scabra,Atractylis_carduus)),(Carlina_gummifera,(Carlina_macrophylla,(Carlina_acanthifolia,(Carlina_brachylepis,((Carlina_falcata,Carlina_lanata),Carlina_vulgaris)))))),Atractylodes_carlinoides)),((((Atractylodes_chinensis_var__liaotungensis,Atractylodes_japonica),Atractylodes_macrocephala),(Oldenburgia_sp__Kaellersjoe_s_n_,((Echinops_onopordum,((Echinops_galaticus,Echinops_sphaerocephalus),(((Echinops_przewalskii,(((Echinops_exaltatus,Echinops_persicus),Echinops_niveus),((Echinops_szovitsii,((Echinops_bannaticus,Echinops_tournefortii),Echinops_ruthenicus)),Echinops_orientalis))),((Echinops_humilis,((Echinops_fontqueri,(Echinops_viscosus,Echinops_bithynicus)),(Echinops_hedgei,(Echinops_cornigerus,Echinops_heteromorphus)))),Echino
